metadata.name: Shall we drink? Luv❤
metadata.description:
This is a fan art of Luv-chan.
Luv-chan is a character designed by Luv (@luvluv_eth).

She is a very pretty pink-haired girl.
She's usually cute and energetic.
This time, I tried to express her adult charm to the fullest in my own way!
You will definitely be thrilled to see a different side of her... ❣
